+# Why You Cannot Fix `sqlite-libs` Vulnerabilities via Code Patching in Containers
+
+This document explains why vulnerabilities like **CVE-2025-29087** in `sqlite-libs` are often **false positives** in containerized environments, and why manual code patching is not a practical or safe solution.
+
+---
+
